metadata.name: UNTOUCHABLE
metadata.description:
From early childhood, we are surrounded by a large number of prohibitions that envelop us on the way to finding our personality, and most often when we are looking for encouragement from society or loved ones, we lose a piece of ourselves, a black shadow remains here instead of the bright colors of our individuality.

Make your inner self untouchable when the whole world is trying to tear you apart, leaving a black spot where the bright colors were.
